{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/gamedev/battleship","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A Python implementation of the classic battleship game.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/b97f6/battleship-name-slaget.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Translating ships\"\n        title=\"Translating ships\"\n        src=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/5a190/battleship-name-slaget.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/772e8/battleship-name-slaget.png 200w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/e17e5/battleship-name-slaget.png 400w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/5a190/battleship-name-slaget.png 800w,\n/static/af1a7360a560e4428c2a7f1316cc8036/b97f6/battleship-name-slaget.png 958w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I decided to be very original with so common name as battleship. I know that Google Translate has about 40 different languages to choose from. I type in \"battle ship\" in English and start peeking different languages on the opposite side and I start tasting how these new words sound like.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/b97f6/battleship-name-bato-yo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Translating ships\"\n        title=\"Translating ships\"\n        src=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/5a190/battleship-name-bato-yo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/772e8/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 200w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/e17e5/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 400w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/5a190/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 800w,\n/static/9f3295bc8c7dece1637aba6b9492f3e3/b97f6/battleship-name-bato-yo.png 958w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>So \"the ships, the battle\" = \"bato yo slaget\". You read it as <strong>BA</strong>rcelona <strong>TO</strong>rtuga <strong>YO</strong>lk <strong>SLA</strong>ck fri<strong>GATE</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 762px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a016c/battleship_main_menu.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Main menu\"\n        title=\"Main menu\"\n        src=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a016c/battleship_main_menu.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/772e8/battleship_main_menu.png 200w,\n/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/e17e5/battleship_main_menu.png 400w,\n/static/c2b77e254814940fa2b1283b9eecb72a/a016c/battleship_main_menu.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>History</h2>\n<p>Basic logic adopted from <strong>@JBKahn</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/JBKahn/Battleship\">code</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/6bfd0/battleship_console.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Console version\"\n        title=\"Console version\"\n        src=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/5a190/battleship_console.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/772e8/battleship_console.png 200w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/e17e5/battleship_console.png 400w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/5a190/battleship_console.png 800w,\n/static/4bd2eccf09a5dad201ff0f238577746a/6bfd0/battleship_console.png 1011w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Features I liked:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>board size is a variable</li>\n<li>amount of players defined at runtime</li>\n<li>user ships can be placed on the board randomly</li>\n<li>simple console output</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 762px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a016c/battleship_positioning.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Positioning\"\n        title=\"Positioning\"\n        src=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a016c/battleship_positioning.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/772e8/battleship_positioning.png 200w,\n/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/e17e5/battleship_positioning.png 400w,\n/static/eb9d4a616410409f1e0da1f070c54b36/a016c/battleship_positioning.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Important things added:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ships can not intersect</li>\n<li>unlimited amount of players (strange feature of course)</li>\n<li>split the monolith code onto small classes (one class - one file)</li>\n<li>game logic in separate python modules</li>\n</ul>\n<p>From <strong>@tmac-balla</strong> I've taken <a href=\"https://github.com/tmac-balla/battleship-game\">the engine</a> that uses PyGame library and </p>\n<ul>\n<li>extended logic classes with sprites and fonts</li>\n<li>linked game classes to the engine</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Current state of development</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 762px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a016c/battleship_gameplay.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gameplay\"\n        title=\"Gameplay\"\n        src=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a016c/battleship_gameplay.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/772e8/battleship_gameplay.png 200w,\n/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/e17e5/battleship_gameplay.png 400w,\n/static/92be825bcbd2f4d6b432eba00d2776aa/a016c/battleship_gameplay.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>game ends when the game ends (just restart the app)</li>\n<li>not stable (auto ship positioning going wild)</li>\n<li>and maybe more...</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mikolasan/bato-yo-slaget\">Github</a></p>\n<h2>Roadmap</h2>\n<p>OK, how to make a regular dead simple Battleship implementation to be more like <strong>Not your father's battleship</strong>?</p>\n<h3>Gameplay ideas</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Not square field (check out <a href=\"http://boardgamegeek.com/thread/605234/bravo-battleship\">this review</a> and read more about <a href=\"http://www.redblobgames.com/grids/hexagons\">hexagons</a>)</li>\n<li>Restoring fog of war plus moving ships</li>\n<li>Ships against coastal defense</li>\n<li>Aircraft carrier (5 cells) - relatively easy to find and sink, but it gives exploration data with some chance to locate one cell ships</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Technical ideas</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Run Python on Android</li>\n<li>Switch to voxel engine</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 762px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/a016c/battleship_win_message.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Win message\"\n        title=\"Win message\"\n        src=\"/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/a016c/battleship_win_message.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/772e8/battleship_win_message.png 200w,\n/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/e17e5/battleship_win_message.png 400w,\n/static/815d521fd48262be348134e948b0df39/a016c/battleship_win_message.png 762w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 762px) 100vw, 762px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 19, 2020","path":"/gamedev/battleship","title":"Battleship","section":null,"draft":null,"subtitle":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","backgroundColor":"#4878b8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0d51580afb4ac18884eaab730db3830d/40e5d/battleship_last_step.png","srcSet":"/static/0d51580afb4ac18884eaab730db3830d/ff0b0/battleship_last_step.png 576w,\n/static/0d51580afb4ac18884eaab730db3830d/40e5d/battleship_last_step.png 762w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0d51580afb4ac18884eaab730db3830d/de17f/battleship_last_step.webp 576w,\n/static/0d51580afb4ac18884eaab730db3830d/2a3cf/battleship_last_step.webp 762w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.9081364829396326}}}}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"pagePath":"/gamedev/battleship","breadcrumb":{"location":"/gamedev/battleship","crumbs":[{"pathname":"/","crumbLabel":"Index"},{"pathname":"/gamedev","crumbLabel":"gamedev"},{"pathname":"/gamedev/battleship","crumbLabel":"battleship"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1291123867","2911207801","3388252522","447685113"]}